@startuml
!theme cerulean
title UC-05 - Activity Diagram: Generate Flat File Output

start

:1. Receive transformed data from Mapping Engine;

:2. Determine Target Format from Integration Profile;

:3. Select Output Writer Strategy 
   (CSV_Xcenter, CSV_Dataloader, XML, etc.);

:4. Apply File Naming Pattern 
   (e.g. ITEM_MASTER_YYYYMMDDHHmm.csv);

:5. Generate file content 
   (Header + Data rows with delimiter);

:6. Write file to output directory;

if (Write successful?) then (Yes)
  :7. Validate file integrity 
     (row count, format check);
  :8. Update processing status = Success;
  :9. Notify Target System (optional);
else (No)
  :Push to DLQ with error details;
  detach
endif

:10. Log audit trail (file name, size, duration);

stop

@enduml